<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 08:11:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国官员：以色列不能等七个月才与哈马斯达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-israel-cannot-afford-to-wait-seven-months-for-a-hostage-deal-with-hamas/0000018f-c611-da41-a9cf-d73f048e0000</link><description>华盛顿的一名高级官员在回应以色列国家安全顾问的评论时表示，“每一天都在增加他们活着回来的可能性”。以色列国家安全顾问声称，战争将至少持续到今年年底。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 03:01:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-israel-cannot-afford-to-wait-seven-months-for-a-hostage-deal-with-hamas/0000018f-c611-da41-a9cf-d73f048e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对党认为，内塔尼亚胡政党叛逃的可能性有所增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-believes-chances-of-defections-from-netanyahus-party-have-increased/0000018f-c64e-d323-a98f-df4fee2f0000</link><description>反对派高级人士瞄准利库德集团五名成员，并提出统一战线，鼓励他们逃跑</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 03:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-believes-chances-of-defections-from-netanyahus-party-have-increased/0000018f-c64e-d323-a98f-df4fee2f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全部门如何拒绝《国土报》关于摩萨德涉嫌勒索国际法院检察官的报告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-nixed-haaretzs-report-into-alleged-mossad-extortion-of-hague-prosecutor/0000018f-c608-d801-a3ef-ff08cf810000</link><description>本周《古尔迪安报》的报道揭露了时任摩萨德主席约西·科恩如何试图扰乱并调查当时的国际刑事法院检察官法图·本苏达。 ■ 2022 年，《国土报》原本打算公布该事件的细节，但安全官员阻止了此事 ■对于以色列来说，这一消息的曝光实在是太糟糕了</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 03:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-nixed-haaretzs-report-into-alleged-mossad-extortion-of-hague-prosecutor/0000018f-c608-d801-a3ef-ff08cf810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列削弱巴勒斯坦权力机构的努力可能会打破西岸有限的平静</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-efforts-to-weaken-the-pa-could-shatter-the-limited-calm-in-the-west-bank/0000018f-c5fe-d801-a3ef-fdfea0810000</link><description>鉴于政府计划采取的行动，以色列面临着开辟新战线的风险 ■ 以色列国防军发现很难应对来自巴勒斯坦城镇对靠近西岸隔离墙的以色列社区的枪击袭击 ■ 数千名预备役军人接受了第三次袭击征召令——但他们中的一些人不得不四处寻找最基本的设备</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 03:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-efforts-to-weaken-the-pa-could-shatter-the-limited-calm-in-the-west-bank/0000018f-c5fe-d801-a3ef-fdfea0810000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列士兵在约旦河西岸汽车撞击袭击中丧生，其中一名在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article-live/two-people-critically-hurt-in-west-bank-ramming-attack-driver-reportedly-surrenders-to-pa/0000018f-c73d-d4da-a58f-f7fd27340000</link><description>对约旦河西岸汽车冲撞袭击事件的初步调查显示，部队未能向逃离现场的司机开枪。因恶劣天气造成损坏的加沙援助码头将被送往阿什杜德进行维修 ■ 以色列国家安全顾问表示，加沙战争将持续到 2024 年</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 02:10:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-30/ty-article-live/two-people-critically-hurt-in-west-bank-ramming-attack-driver-reportedly-surrenders-to-pa/0000018f-c73d-d4da-a58f-f7fd27340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的“高强度”行动即将结束。但内塔尼亚胡不希望加沙战争结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-intense-operations-are-almost-over-but-netanyahu-doesnt-want-the-war-to-end/0000018f-c57d-da41-a9cf-d57f55370000</link><description>以色列政治或军事机构中没有人认为加沙战争即将结束。但内塔尼亚胡不会谈论停火，甚至不会将人质带回家，也不会谈论停火后的第二天，他当然不会听到任何有关提前选举的谈论</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-intense-operations-are-almost-over-but-netanyahu-doesnt-want-the-war-to-end/0000018f-c57d-da41-a9cf-d57f55370000</guid></item><item><title>工作日有道路施工吗？以色列交通运输部副部长解释公众将如何获得补偿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/roadworks-on-weekdays-deputy-transport-minister-explains-how-public-will-be-compensated/0000018f-c4b1-d323-a98f-dff96ab50000</link><description>特拉维夫至耶路撒冷 1 号高速公路将在下周而不是周末关闭，极端正统派交通运输部副部长乌里·马克列夫 (Uri Maklev) 表示，“我们将通过加强对安息日的遵守来补偿以色列人”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/roadworks-on-weekdays-deputy-transport-minister-explains-how-public-will-be-compensated/0000018f-c4b1-d323-a98f-dff96ab50000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：以色列战时联盟出现裂痕，甘茨对内塔尼亚胡的领先优势缩小</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/poll-gantzs-lead-over-netanyahu-narrows-as-wartime-coalition-shows-cracks/0000018f-c5b8-d323-a98f-dff9cfdc0000</link><description>受访者被问及他们认为谁更适合担任总理，在所有比较中，内塔尼亚胡领先</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:43:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/poll-gantzs-lead-over-netanyahu-narrows-as-wartime-coalition-shows-cracks/0000018f-c5b8-d323-a98f-dff9cfdc0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日左右，与杰里·宋飞 (Jerry Seinfeld) 一起哭泣。但请为加沙人留一滴眼泪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-29/ty-article/.highlight/cry-with-jerry-seinfeld-about-october-7-but-save-a-tear-for-the-gazans/0000018f-c579-db12-a3ff-c77fc0b40000</link><description>巴里·韦斯和宋飞正需要多少同理心才能停下来，认为也许“暴民”（他们在《自由新闻》采访中提到亲巴勒斯坦运动）也正承受着痛苦，但我仍然惊讶的是他们俩都无法鼓起勇气</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 18:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-29/ty-article/.highlight/cry-with-jerry-seinfeld-about-october-7-but-save-a-tear-for-the-gazans/0000018f-c579-db12-a3ff-c77fc0b40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称已控制加沙-埃及边境战略走廊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/israeli-army-says-it-took-control-of-strategic-corridor-along-gaza-egypt-border/0000018f-c56a-d8a8-afff-effe50780000</link><description>这条非军事化的狭窄走廊横跨埃及边境加沙一侧，全长 14 公里；以色列国防军还承认，尚未完全控制加沙地带北部</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 17:59:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/israeli-army-says-it-took-control-of-strategic-corridor-along-gaza-egypt-border/0000018f-c56a-d8a8-afff-effe50780000</guid></item><item><title>“需要紧急选举”：加沙战争内阁部长猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡；总理：他们希望结束战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/urgent-elections-needed-war-cabinet-ministers-slam-netanyahu-pm-they-want-to-end-war/0000018f-c4ee-db12-a3ff-c7fe72510000</link><description>中间派战时内阁成员加迪·艾森科特表示，总理对加沙的成就“宣扬虚假的妄想”，并且“惨败”地实现了目标</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 16:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/urgent-elections-needed-war-cabinet-ministers-slam-netanyahu-pm-they-want-to-end-war/0000018f-c4ee-db12-a3ff-c7fe72510000</guid></item><item><title>“犹太复国主义者到达之前，帕洛阿尔托要好得多”：斯坦福大学加沙营地的一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palo-alto-was-much-nicer-before-the-zionists-came-a-day-at-stanfords-gaza-encampment/0000018f-c4c9-d4da-a58f-f7d9191c0000</link><description>在该大学的抗议现场，一位最近称哈马斯和真主党为“荣誉人物”的奥克兰伊玛目对一名亲以色列的犹太学生说：“你们都变得像纳粹了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 16:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palo-alto-was-much-nicer-before-the-zionists-came-a-day-at-stanfords-gaza-encampment/0000018f-c4c9-d4da-a58f-f7d9191c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴西总统召回驻以色列大使 加沙战争外交危机加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/brazils-president-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-intensifying-diplomatic-crisis-over-gaza/0000018f-c4e6-d4da-a58f-f7ff7f6b0000</link><description>巴西官员表示，此次召回是由于以色列对大使的“羞辱”，当时以色列外交部长传唤他强制参观大屠杀纪念馆，以谴责卢拉总统将加沙攻势与大屠杀相比较的言论</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 16:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/brazils-president-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-intensifying-diplomatic-crisis-over-gaza/0000018f-c4e6-d4da-a58f-f7ff7f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>请欢迎您的新室友“老大哥”：一名被关押在加沙的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/welcome-your-new-big-brother-housemates-israelis-held-in-gaza/0000018f-c3bf-de7a-a5df-c3ff592f0000</link><description>以色列版真人秀节目《老大哥》新一季回归。令人不安的在线活动确保你无法逃避现实</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:45:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/welcome-your-new-big-brother-housemates-israelis-held-in-gaza/0000018f-c3bf-de7a-a5df-c3ff592f0000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡和以色列回答这三个问题之前，加沙战争不会结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-wont-end-until-netanyahu-and-israel-answer-these-three-questions/0000018f-c3db-dbf7-adef-e3fb1ba70000</link><description>问题很尖锐。首先，加沙战争会结束吗？如何结束？之后会发生什么？以色列和巴勒斯坦人未来必须何去何从才能确保这种地狱不再重演？每个问题都有一个选择和一个答案</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-wont-end-until-netanyahu-and-israel-answer-these-three-questions/0000018f-c3db-dbf7-adef-e3fb1ba70000</guid></item><item><title>七名以色列警察因在巴勒斯坦人脸上盖上大卫之星而受到审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-cops-expected-to-be-tried-for-stamping-star-of-david-on-palestinians-face/0000018f-c41d-d0b7-abdf-ccbfd4d30000</link><description>参与逮捕东耶路撒冷难民营 22 岁居民的警官涉嫌虐待、严重袭击、妨碍司法公正和其他罪行</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:48:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-cops-expected-to-be-tried-for-stamping-star-of-david-on-palestinians-face/0000018f-c41d-d0b7-abdf-ccbfd4d30000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列士兵在拉法爆炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-rafah/0000018f-c457-d4da-a58f-f7df5f310000</link><description>这些士兵是参谋军士。阿米尔·加利洛夫，20 岁，参谋军士。乌里·巴尔·奥尔（Uri Bar Or）和参谋中士。伊多·阿佩尔，21 岁</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-rafah/0000018f-c457-d4da-a58f-f7df5f310000</guid></item><item><title>西班牙承认巴勒斯坦，内塔尼亚胡在以色列欢迎西班牙反伊斯兰党领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-welcomes-spanish-anti-islam-party-leader-in-israel-as-spain-recognized-palestine/0000018f-c484-da41-a9cf-d5bef18a0000</link><description>西班牙极右翼 Vox 党领袖圣地亚哥·阿巴斯卡 (Santiago Abascal) 因伊斯兰恐惧症、反移民言论和反 LGBTQ 立场而受到批评，他来到以色列会见内塔尼亚胡，谴责西班牙左翼政府</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-welcomes-spanish-anti-islam-party-leader-in-israel-as-spain-recognized-palestine/0000018f-c484-da41-a9cf-d5bef18a0000</guid></item><item><title>汉娜·阿伦特将如何回应以色列被指控犯有反人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-hannah-arendt-would-respond-to-israel-being-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-c3e2-d822-a58f-d7fe35a90000</link><description>阿伦特逃离了纳粹，并因报道艾希曼审判而闻名，他坚信国际刑事法院可以防止种族灭绝。那么她会支持国际刑事法院对以色列和哈马斯领导人发出的潜在逮捕令吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 12:58:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-hannah-arendt-would-respond-to-israel-being-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-c3e2-d822-a58f-d7fe35a90000</guid></item><item><title>妮基·黑利在以色列军队炮弹上涂写暴力信息，引发愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/nikki-haley-scrawls-violent-message-on-idf-artillery-shell-sparks-criticism/0000018f-c413-de7a-a5df-c77f50da0000</link><description>在参观10月7日以色列南部遭到袭击的地点时，失败的共和党总统候选人加入了签署以色列国防军导弹的潮流。 “你能带她回去吗？”一位和平活动人士反驳道，“我们已经有了一个本-格维尔”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 12:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/nikki-haley-scrawls-violent-message-on-idf-artillery-shell-sparks-criticism/0000018f-c413-de7a-a5df-c77f50da0000</guid></item></channel></rss>